 grime with its tail can be helpful when cleaning. But its focus on spotlessness can make cleaning more of a hassle."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "When its tail has gotten dirty from self-cleaning or from cleaning its nest, Minccino spends a whole day washing its tail in clean spring water."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "A clean freak that will not allow even the slightest mess, it uses its tail like a mop to thoroughly clean any and all filth."}, {"version": "white", "text": "These Pok\u00e9mon prefer a tidy habitat. They are always sweeping and dusting, using their tails as brooms."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "Minccino greet each other by grooming one another thoroughly with their tails."}, {"version": "x", "text": "Minccino greet each other by grooming one another thoroughly with their tails."}, {"version": "y", "text": "These Pok\u00e9mon prefer a tidy habitat. They are always sweeping and dusting, using their tails as brooms."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "minccino"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "cinccino"}]}